name: The Preston Ep
description:
With the hard copy you receive an extra copy of the sleeve cover ,of my eye! 

Stick it on your fridge, put it on your wall; but for god sake before you do that, take a photo  holding it to your eye; and send to my facebook.com/ricbirtill

Enjoy.






Ric Birtill- The Preston Ep 

The Preston Ep is based on and inspired by life in Preston, Lancashire. It features 5 songs about religion, romance, employment, agoraphobia and alcohol - dependence.
